  "summary": "Mattermost doesn't filter nil elements from outgoing webhook attachment payloads before processing",
  "details": "Mattermost versions 11.6.x \u003c= 11.6.0, 11.5.x \u003c= 11.5.3, 11.4.x \u003c= 11.4.4, 10.11.x \u003c= 10.11.14 fail to filter nil elements from outgoing webhook attachment payloads before processing, which allows an authenticated user to cause a denial of service (server process termination) via a crafted webhook callback response containing a null attachment entry. Mattermost Advisory ID: MMSA-2026-00641",
